{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Ark Odyssey</strong> is a top-down arcade shooter that lets you command an army of starships to fight against the force of void!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You will be able to recruit a wide variety of starship squadrons, each one having a unique design and origin, custom passive, attack pattern, and special abilities! Build your very own fleet of unique squadrons by freely customizing unit composition into each different formation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Become a tactician on the battlefield, shift between different formations in combat for greater advantage, and focus fire with your squadron at crucial moments to turn the tides of battle!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2995590/extras/NewGameplay.gif?t=1728818393\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2995590/extras/EzGameplay.gif?t=1728818393\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2995590/extras/CombatGameplay-ezgif.com-optimize.gif?t=1728818393\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Key Feature</strong></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Create a unique build of fun and dazzling fleet of starships.</strong> With more than 50+ unique squadrons of starships and 100+ artifacts, you will be able to assemble your very own different army each run.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2995590/extras/InterfaceGameplay-ezgif.com-optimize.gif?t=1728818393\" /></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Highly customizable team building.</strong> Freely adjust unit composition for each different formation, plan attack order a